<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.7.6">
<l>kallāl kaṭalai yaṇaikaṭ ṭiyukantāy</l>
<l>nallār palarvē tiyarmaṉ ṉiyanāṅkūr</l>
<l>celvā tiruveḷ ḷa<supplied>k</supplied>kuḷat  tuṟaivāṉē,</l>
<l>yellā viṭaruṅ keṭumā ṟaruḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who was pleased having built a dam of the sea with stones,</l>
<l>Noble of Nāṅkūr where many good people [and] Vedic experts dwell,</l>
<l>One who dwells in Tiruveḷḷakkuḷam,</l>
<l>Be gracious in a way that all suffering is destroyed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
